<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.itch.billwoo.RiseOfThePenguinsGB</id>

  <name>Rise of the Penguins GB</name>
  <summary>A retro penguin platformer designed for Gameboy. Perfect for fans of penguins and anyone looking for a moderate challenge in a cold setting!</summary>

  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>LicenseRef-proprietary</project_license>

  <developer id="io.itch.billwoo">
    <name>billwoo</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      Rise of the Penguins is a 2D side-scrolling action-platformer for Gameboy. 
      The game is meant to be simple and linear but with some challenging enemies. 
      Inspired by Ghost n Goblins and a bit of Mega Man.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>6 levels with a variety of enemies in each level</li>
      <li>2 extra levels</li>
      <li>Boss Rush Mode - unlocked after beating all 6 levels</li>
      <li>6 mini boss enemies and 8 boss enemies plus a final boss</li>
      <li>6 difficulty settings to adjust checkpoints - make the game harder or easier</li>
      <li>Basic HUD showing highscore, health and time remaining</li>
      <li>Minimal story with no text - engaging gameplay keeps you playing</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

